description: Off the Hook is a great Birmingham-based truck dedicated to serving the tastiest seafood sandwiches, tacos, and sliders fast and fresh to you! Find them on our map whenever they tweet their location in and around Birmingham's downtown area, and grab a taste of this amazing food for yourself. Or, if you have a special event that needs this truck's fantastic flair, have them whip up a catering menu perfect to suit your needs. Just think about mouthwatering shrimp poboys, crab sliders, rocket shrimp, or fish and chips, and tell us... are you hooked yet?
name: Off The Hook
